!! Adverb inflection
!! ---------------
!! Komi adverbs inflect for direction.


LEXICON Ad-ATAG ! these are checked as advs.
+AdA: # ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_GER-IGON ! these are checked as gerunds in +Der/иг
+V+Der/иг+Instr: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_GER-IGTYRJI ! these are checked as gerunds in +Der/иг
+V+Der/иг+Der/тырйи: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_GER-MON ! these are checked as gerunds in +Der/мӧн
+V+Der/мӧн: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_GER-TOG ! these are checked as gerunds in +Der/тӧг
+V+Der/тӧг: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_GER-TODZ ! these are checked as gerunds in +Der/тӧдз
+V+Der/тӧдз: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_N-TOG ! these are checked as state adverbials in +Der/тӧг
+N+Der/тӧг: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_ADV-TOG ! polar adverbials in +Der/тӧг
+Adv+Der/тӧг: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_Q-TOG ! polar adverbials in +Der/тӧг
+Qnt+Der/тӧг: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-IS_SUPERL !
+Der/мед: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-F !
+Src/F: ADVTAG ;

LEXICON ADV-STATE !
+Adv+State: COMPARATIVE ; !

LEXICON AdvParenthetic
+Adv+Parenthetic: # ;

LEXICON ADVTAG ! these are checked as advs.
+Adv: COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT ! these are adverbs in spatial cases
      !and they probably are equivalent in morphology to postpositions
 ADV-SPAT-APR ;
 ADV-SPAT-APRILL ;
 ADV-SPAT-APRINE ;
 ADV-SPAT-APRELA ;
 ADV-SPAT-EGR ;
 ADV-SPAT-ELA ;
 ADV-SPAT-ILL ;
 ADV-SPAT-INE ;
 ADV-SPAT-PRL ;
 ADV-SPAT-TER ;
 ADV-SPAT-TRA ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-LA ! These adverbs have a formative in ла
+Der/ла: ADV-SPAT ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-APR
+Adv+Spat+Apr:%>лань SPAT-COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-APRELA
+Adv+Spat+Apr:%>ланьысь SPAT-COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-APRILL
