LEXICON ADV-SPAT-EGR
+Adv+Spat+Egr:%>сянь SPAT-COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-ELA
+Adv+Spat+Ela:%>ысь SPAT-COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-ILL
+Adv+Spat+Ill:%>ӧ SPAT-COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-INE
+Adv+Spat+Ine:%>ын SPAT-COMPARATIVE ;

LEXICON ADV-SPAT-PRL
